 "UrduImage": null, "IsRed": 0, "MinimizeDescriptionLine": 0, "IsPrintable": 0}, {"Id": 1016001, "EnglishTitle": null, "GujaratiTitle": null, "RUrduTitle": null, "UrduTitle": null, "Sequence": null, "EnglishDescription": null, "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": null, "UrduDescription": null, "English": "INSHA-ALLAH COMING SOON", "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": "Nekiyo’n mein izaafa farma aur meri buraaiyo’n ka kaffaara qaraar de, be-shak Tu har cheez par qaadir hai. Parwardigaar! Muhammad (s.a.w.a) wa Aale Muhammad (a.s) par durood o rehmat naazil farma.", "Urdu": "نیکیوں میں اضافہ فرما اور میری برائیوں کا کفارہ قرار دے بے شک تو ہر چیز پر قادر ہے۔ پروردگار! محمدؐ و آل محمدؑ پرو درود و رحمت نازل فرما۔", "RArabic": "WA HASANAA-TIN MOZAA-A’FAA-TIN WA KAFFIR A’NNIS SAYYE-AATE INNA-KA A’LAA KULLE SHAY-IN QADEE-RUN ALLAAHUMMA SALLE A’LAA MOHAMMADIN WA AALE MOHAMMADIN.", "ArabicText1": "وَحَسَنَاتٍ مُضَاعَفَاتٍ وَكَفِّرْ عَنِّیْ السَّیِّئَاتِ اِنَّكَ عَلٰی كُلِّ شَیْءٍ قَدِیْرٌ۔ اَللّٰہُمَّ صَلِّ عَلٰی مُحَمَّدٍ وَآلِ مُحَمَّدٍ۔", "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign